works for a graph of 100 nodes in each slave
6 slaves +1 master
query of 7 constraints on edges

arguments:
	arg0: number of sources
	arg1: number of targets

if you want to scale to another size of graph change
replace 100 by the number of nodes per slave
replace 600 by the number of nodes per slave*6
replace the directories to connect to neo4j

in LocalReachability HashSet<Integer> was replaced by an array of boolean 

